53128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:11.000Z","msg":"Why not both"},{"pid":"3f08b5014a02db27a39671e0a9cbb065fd4556fd","tid":1632271,"uid":235100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:15.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"395f80d9887743e0db66d23515d950ebd6fb69a2","tid":1632271,"uid":235100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:38.000Z","msg":"10/10 大家幫推 我推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5959113cb81a3c75c05681bc0634e65aee676e52","tid":1632271,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:52.000Z","msg":"話你知咩叫和勇合一<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630017\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630017</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"acd038504d0277cae005f1ef3861109764e2e2fc","tid":1632271,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"c4a9fc8f692d6223a980f5a5f364e302317cbe89","tid":1632271,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:03.000Z","msg":"聽日一撚定要夜晚18區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629580\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d5b7011b462c5de76401f5ec98191d472d39bad3","tid":1632271,"uid":212843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:14.000Z","msg":"3點"},{"pid":"19350591d0b5a39165c4ee76cae3d09d352ccb33","tid":1632271,"uid":235100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:34.000Z","msg":"投票投票投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3fe22859dd8a8f4f3c6ab9301442f8e039db074","tid":1632271,"uid":235100,"li